getHealthClaims:
Retrieve all medicine-related posts (including tweets, podcasts, vlogs, etc.) by <name> that contain claims about health embedded within the content, example: "Viewing sunlight within 30-60 minutes of waking enhances cortisol release."

For each affirmation, extract and list the following information in this format:

{
  "claims": [
    {
      "claim": "<extracted health affirmation>",
      "datePosted": "<date of the post>",
      "categories": ["<category1>", "<category2>", ...]
    }
  ]
}

Ensure that the claims are presented as simple, short sentences with their corresponding date posted and relevant category names (e.g., Nutrition, Medicine, Mental Health).
